        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Tesla 新款 Model Y 香港登场，内外重新设计科技感更强</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/tesla-model-y-hk-launch/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-model-y-hk-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/tesla-model-y-hk-launch/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 05:35:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Model Y]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290431</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla 宣布在港推出全新 Model Y，率先在启德 AIRSIDE 地下露天广场公开亮相右軚版新车，并由即日起在启德、荃湾及沙田体验中心展出。后轮驱动版「一换一」计划后售价为 HK$339,798，最快 2025 年第二季交付。</p><h3><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-5-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-5-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>这次新推出的「Launch Series」首发限量版，在车尾箱、门槛板及充电中控台等位置加入专属徽章，并设有投影灯，每次开关车门时，徽章图案会投影到地面。全轮驱动版本更额外免费配备加速提升功能，0-100 公里加速时间由 4.8 秒缩短至 4.3 秒，驾驶体验更强劲。这款特别版数量有限，售完即止。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>全新 Model Y 重新设计外观及内饰，新增「冰川蓝」车色，并采用 Cybertruck 及 Cybercab 设计灵感的贯穿式头灯，车尾灯更为业界首创的间接反射式设计，令车身线条更具科技感。车厢则配备双层隔音玻璃，全景玻璃车顶能阻隔 7 倍紫外线及热能，提供更安静舒适的乘坐体验。车轮与尾扰流器经过改良，减低空气阻力，而悬挂系统重新调校后，行驶更平稳顺畅。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><h3></h3><p>长续航版本设有 16 个扬声器及重低音单元，后轮驱动版本则配备 9 个扬声器。此外，新车亦配备 8 吋后排触控萤幕，支援 YouTube、Spotify、Apple Music 及 TIDAL 串流功能，让后排乘客享受更优质的娱乐体验。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newmodelylaunchevent-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>全新 Model Y 充电效能提升，使用 V3 或 V4 超级充电器，15 分钟内可补充 266 公里续航里程，相当于来回荃湾与启德体验中心 10 次。Tesla 目前在香港设有 84 个超级充电站（共 445 个超级充电器）及 134 个目的地充电站（共 1,099 个充电器），覆盖全港 18 区，并维持 99.9% 可用率，确保车主能随时充电。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/my-694x222.png" alt="" width="694" height="222" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/my-694x222.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/my.png 779w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>来源: tesla 新闻稿</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
