        <item>
            <title>Samsung S25U 屏幕更襟跌？有片为证跌落测试 1 米以上仍生还屏幕无损</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/samsung-s25ultra-screen-more-durable-from-drop-test/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-s25ultra-screen-more-durable-from-drop-test</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/samsung-s25ultra-screen-more-durable-from-drop-test/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 03:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Drop Test]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy S25 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290414</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>对于不少手机用家来说，相信「用家最痛」肯定是手机跌落屏幕，虽说近年不少手机屏幕均更耐刮，但一旦不慎跌落石屎地，屏幕可以完美生还的手机在现今市场中亦确实不多。最近 Samsung 推出的旗舰手机 Galaxy S25 Ultra，就有外媒进行了跌落测试，结果确实有点惊喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290416" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-1-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-1-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-2-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-2-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-3-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-3-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>其实官方在发布 Galaxy S25 Ultra 时已表明新机采用了全新，由 Corning 制造的新一代强化玻璃 Gorilla Armor 2 保护它的 6.9 吋 Dynamic AMOLED 2X 荧幕，虽然早前有外媒测试过它的耐刮程度不及上代 Galaxy S24 Ultra，但今日的跌落测试，测试者将 S25 Ultra 以不同角度从 1 米以上数次将 S25 Ultra 跌落石屎硬地，最后似乎也只是它的钛金属边框有少许擦损，而荧幕在数次石屎硬地跌落测试后依然可以生还，而且更是完好无损，结果确实十分有惊喜。看来各位 S25 Ultra 的用家，最多也只需要入手玻璃贴加强防刮效果，对手机的防护应该已十分足够了。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_64776"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MivFjQOXQCM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MivFjQOXQCM&amp;t=267s">PBKreviews</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
