        <item>
            <title>【实试】《Monster Hunter Wilds》Benchmark    4K 要咩卡先够玩？手提机玩得起吗？</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/monster-hunter-wilds-3/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=monster-hunter-wilds-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/monster-hunter-wilds-3/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:41:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏评测]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290349</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>世纪大作《Monster Hunter Wilds》今个月尾就要推出了，既是多平台作品，PC 玩家相信也有不少的吧，有很多玩家已为这游戏而计划著升级大计，而最近 Capcom 推出了<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/2246340/view/547852302920187994">《Monster Hunter Wilds》的 PC 版独立 Benchmark 工具</a>，在 Steam 上免费下载，小编也非常心急，到底自己家中的电脑是否需要升级才可畅玩呢？手提机玩又如何呢？4K 画面的话要什么卡才可以够玩？立即为大家测试一下。</p><p><a title="Steam 6_2_2025 18_34_22" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310225176/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310225176_c5f998b1f1_b.jpg" alt="Steam 6_2_2025 18_34_22" width="1024" height="589" /></a></p><p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》的测试 Benchmark 工具，一推出之后在短短一天内，Steam 上已达到 48,931 人同时在线纪录，可见众多玩家都非常之想知道自己部机跑不跑不动，又或者刚推出的 NVIDIA RTX 50 系新卡玩此游戏又会有几多 FPS，更有趣的，有时会见到一些用家 Post 出自己旧电脑用上 10 年前的显卡的跑分结果。</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark Steam Charts (App 3424520) · SteamDB - Google Chrome 6_2_2025 18_32_46" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310646945/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310646945_a444e79994_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark Steam Charts (App 3424520) · SteamDB - Google Chrome 6_2_2025 18_32_46" width="973" height="660" /></a></p><h2>测试 1：4K 画质用咩卡才够顺够靓？</h2><p>玩《Monster Hunter Wilds》当然个个都想又够顺够靓啦，在 4K 画质下，原来对 PC 的要求都几高的，请看看以下的三项 4K 画面的测试情况。</p><p><a title="_DSC7005" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310720975/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310720975_8e5622978a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7005" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><h2>测试平台</h2><p>CPU：Intel Core Ultra 9 285K<br />
MB：ROG MAXIMUS Z890 EXTREME<br />
RAM：KLEVV CRAS V RGB ROG Certified D5-7200 32GB Kit<br />
SSD：Samsung 980 PRO PCle 4.0 NVMe M.2 1TB<br />
PSU：ROG Thor III 1200W<br />
Cooler：ROG RYUJIN III 360 ARGB EXTREME<br />
FAN：ASUS TUF Gaming TR120 ARGB Reverse FAN<br />
Case：ASUS TUF Gaming GT502 Horizon</p><p>(鸣谢 ASUS 提供测试平台)</p><p><a title="_DSC6989" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54292810550/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54292810550_87615c8da0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6989" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC6963" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54292619109/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54292619109_53ce491a4b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6963" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><h2>4K 画面 + 画格生成</h2><p>测试结果：小编先测试 4K 画面中，画质设定为极高，Frame Gen On，光追 Off，在此极好画面设定下，RTX 4080，RTX 4090，RTX 5080 三张卡的表现都相当顺畅。</p><p><a title="_DSC6790" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54292619444/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54292619444_563e5a2c0f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6790" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">RTX 5080 就以 ASUS Astral RTX 5080 OC Edition 作为测试。</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 3_55_12 PM" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54309500917/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54309500917_619bc70153_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 3_55_12 PM" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><a title="snap0117" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310792325/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310792325_e7b2809796_b.jpg" alt="snap0117" width="1024" height="620" /></a></p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 4_03_10 PM" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310401881/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310401881_3e85ffa2ed_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 4_03_10 PM" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">ASUS Astral RTX 5080 OC Edition 的表现非常理想。</p><h2>4K 画面 + 光追 + 画格生成</h2><p>测试结果：之后就测试 4K 画面中，画质设定为极高，Frame Gen On，光追今次都 On，RTX 4080，RTX 4090，RTX 5080 三张卡的 FPS 的跌幅都很少，只有大约 6% 左右，效果都相当顺畅。</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 4_04_19 PM" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310832035/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310832035_5741645255_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 4_04_19 PM" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><a title="snap0119" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310807340/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310807340_f7813e158c_b.jpg" alt="snap0119" width="1024" height="614" /></a></p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 4_10_58 PM" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54309532597/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54309532597_bd25643303_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 4_10_58 PM" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><h2>4K 画面 + 光追 off + 画格生成 off</h2><p>测试结果：由于有时玩家不喜爱用画格生成，惊有时会出现怪异画面，于是最后再试多一个无画格生成情况下如何，未有画格生成支援下，三卡的 FPS 跌幅都几大，值得留意的是没有画格生成后，RTX 4090 的表现会比 RTX 5080 稍为好。</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 6_19_21 PM" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54309535097/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54309535097_2e6c4a6e46_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 6_19_21 PM" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="snap0120" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310637348/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310637348_d0e1326153_b.jpg" alt="snap0120" width="1024" height="619" /></a></p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 6_35_28 PM" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310646059/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310646059_2011597601_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 2_6_2025 6_35_28 PM" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>小结论：如果你追求 4K 解像度，在极高画质设定下，起码要 RTX 4080，或以上级数的卡才可以够顺够玩。</p><h2>测试 2：用 mini PC 玩得起吗？</h2><p>当然不是指文书机的 mini PC 吧，现时市面上有不少为游戏而设的 mini PC，例如小编手上这部 Minisforum AtomMan G7 Ti，机身纤幼，规格都非常不错的，硬件配置为 i9-14900HX, RTX 4070 8GB, 1TB/32GB RAM，又试试它玩 4K 及 1080P 解像度的表现如何。</p><p><a title="_DSC7004" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310721055/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310721055_3371d2251c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7004" width="683" height="1024" /></a></p><p>测试结果：在 4K 解像度，画质设定为高，DLSS + Frame Gen On，没有开光追情况下，表现都绝不差，有 41FPS。</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 5_2_2025 21_31_28" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54309470192/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54309470192_d0e88a0790_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 5_2_2025 21_31_28" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>测试结果：之后再设定画面为 1080P 解像度，画质设定为高，DLSS + Frame Gen On，没有开光追情况下，表现就很畅顺不错了，有 77FPS。</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 5_2_2025 22_39_20" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310600068/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310600068_d54ed4da1d_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 5_2_2025 22_39_20" width="1024" height="576" /></a><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 5_2_2025 22_21_44" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310357686/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310357686_093635a5e2_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 5_2_2025 22_21_44" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">1080P，画质设定为高，无开光追下，表现不错。</p><p>小结论：以游戏为主的 Mini PC，在应付 1080P 解像度高画质，绝对应付到；但 4K 画面就会有点吃力了。</p><h2>测试３：手提游戏机玩得起吗？</h2><p>测试结果：现时的手提游戏机玩《Monster Hunter Wilds》，小编绝不乐观，以手上的 Steam Deck OLED ，用 800P 的解像度，画面设定为低，平均只有 47 FPS，但要先说明，这个 Benchmark 要 Run 几次才有一次运气好，可以完全执行完成；有好多时会出现弹 Game 情况的；之后再 Set 低一点解像度试试，就算再 Reboot 多次，都未有一次能成功完全运行完成 Benchmark，然而画面在低及极低画质下，真的是很难接受，小编绝不建议用现时的手提机去玩；还是等新一代的手提机再谈吧。</p><p><a title="b72bc64e-b879-43c2-8499-db2bc9e32fbe" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310422206/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310422206_fc9fcd056b_b.jpg" alt="b72bc64e-b879-43c2-8499-db2bc9e32fbe" width="1024" height="768" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">要执行数次才有一次成功通过 Benchmark&#8230;</p><p><a title="e5203d6c-08e8-4f15-b5be-f9033412cfec" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310667863/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310667863_a570a2d518_b.jpg" alt="e5203d6c-08e8-4f15-b5be-f9033412cfec" width="1024" height="768" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">画面设定为低后，画面可以说惨不忍睹&#8230;&#8230;</p><p><a title="d52bd064-d626-4946-b488-5fb778b8e40e" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310653124/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310653124_4a849c15db_b.jpg" alt="d52bd064-d626-4946-b488-5fb778b8e40e" width="1024" height="768" /></a></p><h2>测试４：4-5 年前的旧电脑玩到吗？</h2><p>小编用 4-5 年前的旧电脑，用 1080P，中画质画面又可以玩吗？</p><p>5 年多前旧电脑规格<br />
CPU：AMD Ryzen 7 2700X<br />
Ram：16GB<br />
Display Card：NVIDIA RTX 3080</p><p>测试结果：竟然又 OK 㖞，速度及画面都可以接受到，暂时不用换新机了！</p><p><a title="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 6_2_2025 9_46_00" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310662639/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310662639_23fbf7d84b_b.jpg" alt="Monster Hunter Wilds Benchmark 6_2_2025 9_46_00" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><h2>测试 5：10 多年前旧电脑测试</h2><p>小编最后想试试 10 多年前的旧电脑，用上 GTX 750 Ti，又跑不跑得动呢？但直接出程序异常，被强制关闭程式&#8230;&#8230;多次 Reboot 都是如此，唯有放弃了。</p><p><a title="snap0116" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310672784/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310672784_84c1d3724a.jpg" alt="snap0116" width="360" height="500" /></a></p><p><a title="snap0115" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54310236116/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54310236116_5ae390a4c6_b.jpg" alt="snap0115" width="928" height="546" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">小编的旧电脑执行时，就出现程式异常，强制终止&#8230;&#8230;</p><p style="text-align: left;">旧电脑规格<br />
CPU：Intel Core i7-4790<br />
Ram：16GB Ram<br />
Display Card： Gigabyte GTX 750Ti</p><p>测试结果：程式错误终止</p><h2>总结：还得看自己的需要决定是否升级</h2><p>今次小编试了多种不同硬件及画质下执行《Monster Hunter Wilds》Benchmark 的情况，咸鱼青菜各有所好，每人的 Budget 也有不同，是否需要升级，还是还可以继续用旧机玩，以上的种种测试，希望能够帮到大家作个参考了。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/monster-hunter-wilds-3/game-channel/">【实试】《Monster Hunter Wilds》Benchmark    4K 要咩卡先够玩？手提机玩得起吗？</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
